{"tid":1754674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有侯任區議員立即成立文宣隊！！！","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:38:09.000Z","uid":9534,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8715c6d15aeeba8b5bd81b5374c2cedf2af80a49","tid":1754674,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"恭喜咁多位區議員手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔該你地咪撚懶，贏左就算</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地依家有388席議席，如果每個議員請1-2個手足每日開街站(政治也好民生也好)，咁全香港每日都可以有過百個街站做文宣攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣工作將會更有組織同更有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當初我地有二百萬人上街都係因為文宣做得好先有既效果，所以文宣戰線絕對唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家黎緊4年可以免費做文宣之餘仲可以幫手解決手足經濟困難，絕對一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n03年泛民班柒頭就係唔撚做野之後4年後輸返晒，我地一定要從錯誤中學習，係社區保持活躍，徹底消滅建制狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推到上熱門比區議員手足睇"},{"pid":"7e4fcaa64d267d15fd03da1deb134b89d5cc15a4","tid":1754674,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"2decbe004a1a02bd4c89732248a7d435f3ff8056","tid":1754674,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"e9caceabd362b6600cf8a9374b0fcc36a8789682","tid":1754674,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為有好多區議員有好多補貼........"},{"pid":"6b26293dea98f671356491f069e28d1c2e37ca39","tid":1754674,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9caceabd362b6600cf8a9374b0fcc36a8789682","tid":1754674,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為有好多區議員有好多補貼........"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"可以搵下有冇街坊肯做義工<br />\n或者淨係lunch同放工開"},{"pid":"8e8681969ae469a08c2514316fdcf623849958ae","tid":1754674,"uid":297578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63c49cbb9c10032b89a84155bac32b31fe773415","tid":1754674,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"86e5dafc5bd49dad71446a2a2da85aa230f61b0f","tid":1754674,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9caceabd362b6600cf8a9374b0fcc36a8789682","tid":1754674,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為有好多區議員有好多補貼........"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"開街站唔需要太高成本 主要要人同印單張姐"},{"pid":"356bc54ba9b0901e8b8d8e435e978b9e9b2e5c81","tid":1754674,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"建議<br />\n- 用1 team人整區報<br />\n將文宣訊息傳入屋內<br />\n- 搵地方永續連儂牆<br />\n同時可以作為一個全民議事嘅地點<br />\n令區內市民有更高參與度"},{"pid":"cb08ed456023cebef2f336a5514850c088f9c7ec","tid":1754674,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356bc54ba9b0901e8b8d8e435e978b9e9b2e5c81","tid":1754674,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"建議<br />\n- 用1 team人整區報<br />\n將文宣訊息傳入屋內<br />\n- 搵地方永續連儂牆<br />\n同時可以作為一個全民議事嘅地點<br />\n令區內市民有更高參與度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"真係有好多突破想像既野可以試下做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dced1b12cdf917dabac11ca0bf26cf0acac4e7f8","tid":1754674,"uid":144492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb08ed456023cebef2f336a5514850c088f9c7ec","tid":1754674,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356bc54ba9b0901e8b8d8e435e978b9e9b2e5c81","tid":1754674,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"建議<br />\n- 用1 team人整區報<br />\n將文宣訊息傳入屋內<br />\n- 搵地方永續連儂牆<br />\n同時可